            "title": "欧洲股市早段上升\r\n",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">      欧洲股市早段上升。英国富时100指数报8,568.26点，升8.93点(0.10%)；德国DAX指数报23,299.97点，升184.01点(0.80%)；法国CAC 40指数报7,653.05点，升26.21点(0.34%)。  (WL)</span>\n</div>",
